*   ## **_Grande Americano def. Dragon Lee with the help of the two other Americanos_**
    

AJ Styles tried to help fight them off but he was not successful.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/7f2b9107-fc07-4c1d-8f8e-e64281eddb9e/16913.jpg)

Lyra Valkyria eavesdrops on Bayley having a fight with herself. It sounds like the Ding Dong Hello heel took out the Hugger face Bayley when Lyra walks in.

Evil Bayley snaps at Lyra asking why wouldn't she knock, what if she was naked?

