![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/6e62f93e-f5a5-4fea-b852-5af22f464b12/processed_16920.jpg)

*   ## **_Stephanie Vaquer def. Kairi Sane_**
    

Asuka comes out to fight Vaquer post match.

Iyo Sky runs out to separate the fight. Backstage, Iyo tells Asuka that she wants to win the title on her own. Asuka tells Iyo that she better win.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/21b7fa62-de53-4578-8ddd-ddec166107ac/16926.png)

*   ## **_The Vision def. LA Knight and Jimmy Uso_**
    

Post match Bronson holds up Jimmy while Bron Breakker Spears him. Jey Uso comes out for the save but LA Knight is holding a chair behind him so Jey freaks out.

All seems good but LA Knight hits Jey Uso with the BFT to close the show

